  "prompt": "Is there any dual SIM mobile supporting 4G or 4G and 3G?",
  "response": "Yes, there are several dual SIM mobile phones that support 4G or a combination of 4G and 3G. Some popular options include:\n\n1. **Samsung Galaxy A52**: This phone supports dual SIM with 4G on both slots.\n2. **Xiaomi Mi 11**: This device also supports dual SIM with 4G on both slots.\n3. ** OnePlus Nord**: It supports dual SIM with 4G on both slots.\n4. **Google Pixel 5**: This phone supports dual SIM with 4G on both slots.\n5. **Huawei P40 Pro**: This device supports dual SIM with 4G on one slot and 3G on the other.\n\nThese are just a few examples, and there are many other options available from various manufacturers. When shopping for a dual SIM phone, make sure to check the specifications to confirm that it supports the desired network speeds on both SIM slots.",
